{"tid":1185435,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(非自駕) 四月冰島17天環島遊","createTime":"2019-06-04T09:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T18:49:09.000Z","uid":64547,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d4d2bc807ccea1e9801882824f5db15cdd089636","tid":1185435,"uid":64547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:21:23.000Z","msg":"呢個post係想分享下比未有車牌但又好想去冰島既朋友 唔自駕靠巴士同hitchhike一樣都可以玩得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n環島方式: 45L Backpack (徒步+ hitchhike + 巴士)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次係半即興 飛前半個月先買機票<br />\n我唔係來回咁買 <br />\n因為本身plan左去其他地方<br />\n所以機票個度買貴左<br />\n後尾睇返二月尾有promotion<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n來回大約 5300-5600左右  <br />\n想係三四月去冰島既朋友可以留意下 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機票: 大約 7500 hkd <br />\n(去程有得揀既話千祈唔好經北京轉機 好大機會會delay 今次我就係因為delay miss左之後既機 要補多張機票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食宿交通雜費：8500hkd / 17日<br />\nBreakdown:<br />\n食 2700 hkd /  住(x16晚) 3850 /  交通 1900 hkd<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3qAGjwC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3qAGjwC.png&h=395670f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NZNQXgL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNZNQXgL.png&h=1d45d499&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KnArvCs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKnArvCs.png&h=e1a8eaf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WNHdU50.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWNHdU50.png&h=45baffd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rpgm3XL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRpgm3XL.png&h=a7449c3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44b9de3079bda8d76a54c0c62e8a2a001f55de4","tid":1185435,"uid":61126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:23:46.000Z","msg":"留名等睇"},{"pid":"9b63a4877abafdd3ecaa7fab007ff0cbb8671561","tid":1185435,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:26:07.000Z","msg":"貼多D相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e52b0daf1a073fb459b04fd397aa6de22cf88cd","tid":1185435,"uid":64547,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T11:43:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><ins>冰島環島路線圖</ins></em> </div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j3mqMKz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj3mqMKz.jpg&h=32a51ccc&s={SIZE}\" /> </div><br />\n多數人唔自駕都會報 local day tour / 3-day South Iceland tour <br />\n但我對 tour 無咩好感 而且好多想去既地方 tour 都唔帶你去<br />\n所以就選擇左徒步/巴士/hitchhike<br />\n至於住宿點揀曬最平既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 括號係有去到既景點<br />\n而有啲出名既景點 (只係 tour 經常提及既) 反而無去，因為時間問題被迫放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ne.g. Keri&eth;, &THORN;ingvellir National Park, Diamond Beach... 不過其實冰島沿途就係風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nD1 Stay Reyjkavik<br />\nD2 Stay Skogar (Seljalandsfoss, Sk&oacute;gafoss, Kvernufoss)<br />\nD3-4 Stay Vik (Solheimasandur Plane Wreck, Reynisfjara Beach, Reynisdrangar Seastacks) <br />\nD5 Stay Hofn (Fja&eth;r&aacute;rglj&uacute;fur CLOSED, Svartifoss, J&ouml;kuls&aacute;rl&oacute;n)<br />\nD6 Stay Egilssta&eth;ir (Vestrahorn, Stokksnes)<br />\nD7-8 Stay M&yacute;vatn (Dettifoss, Hverfjall)<br />\nD9 Stay Akureyri (Go&eth;afoss)<br />\nD10-11 Stay Rif (Borgarnes, Shark Museum, Kolgrafafj&ouml;dur, Kirkjufell, Skar&eth;sv&iacute;k Beach, &Ouml;ndver&eth;arnes lighthouse)<br />\nD12 Stay Laugarvatn<br />\nD13 Stay &Aacute;rnes (Bruarfoss, Geysir, Gullfoss)<br />\nD14-16 Stay Rejkavik (Hjalparfoss, &THORN;j&oacute;&eth;veldisb&aelig;rinn St&ouml;ng)<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿</div><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Day 1-2</strong><br />\n到埗當日已經係黃昏無咩影相<br />\n第二朝計劃搭 0655 既 Straeto Bus南下 <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yp3gTEu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYp3gTEu.png&h=c1986c5e&s={SIZE}\" /> </div><br />\n<br />\n點知去到完全搵唔到巴士站 然後眼白白睇住架巴士係某個角落出現駛去公路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n只好唯有行去下一個巴士站搭0900既班次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FU9sfT6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFU9sfT6.png&h=db588233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6MJApOC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6MJApOC.jpg&h=61e95ff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qwxNfVe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqwxNfVe.jpg&h=069bbbc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yTtwHBq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyTtwHBq.jpg&h=3512a51a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EVSmknZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEVSmknZ.jpg&h=902edc94&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"0ecee3ebf6a1f12abef56837cefc20e0f85e543a","tid":1185435,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T14:26:48.000Z","msg":"好靚<br />\n會唔會好凍？backpack有啲咩？"},{"pid":"67db23f5be17ec8080ef57206c32bc32b5deb7d0","tid":1185435,"uid":77332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T14:27:52.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"8af2dcd242debd6f59fed6d8a16ef732bbdf8842","tid":1185435,"uid":6800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T14:41:38.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n二月去咗十日剩係南部+西島<br />\n真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想夏天再去環島<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320747c6373814b4f33bfa43dd7e4e5ba3e2c938","tid":1185435,"uid":176657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:22:50.000Z","msg":"lm 好想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c61cbe3645654ae6513e1f9fc419dcdeafc778e4","tid":1185435,"uid":205275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T17:54:33.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身已經好中意冰島 再加上最近中意一隊冰島band搞到好想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb036c78e5eb24cb1a1619e18d53c8bff25aea9c","tid":1185435,"uid":25857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T17:55:16.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"94fa731a33f058cadc0c0ace4da09e2ba70fa8d3","tid":1185435,"uid":217024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T18:29:06.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"09df7e95408ff90bd3981a1860617abc03986bf9","tid":1185435,"uid":181720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T02:35:50.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d114ddec4c628b6d79b3d4aea82b74f04fb1e0f","tid":1185435,"uid":64547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ecee3ebf6a1f12abef56837cefc20e0f85e543a","tid":1185435,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T14:26:48.000Z","msg":"好靚<br />\n會唔會好凍？backpack有啲咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T09:56:49.000Z","msg":"溫度唔算特別低 <br />\n四月初南部大約 3 至 8 度 但吹東/南風 (濕凍) 風勢蠻強 平均約35km/h 有幾日去到50幾km/h<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我有鼻敏感所以一係戶外鼻水基本上係無停過 與風雨作戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至於渣車既朋友就唔洗擔心啦</span> <br />\n北部就再凍少少朝早大約去到 -3 度不過可能位處內陸感覺上差唔多 <br />\n去到四月中溫度平均 5-10 度 <br />\n西部同 GOLDEN CIRCLE 都係差唔多 (衣著無變 流鼻水情況暫緩) <br />\n<br />\n衣著方面採用洋蔥式著法  <br />\n- GORTEX 風褸 + Fleece Vest+ 普通 cotton top + merino top x1+ heat tech x1<br />\n- waterproof shorts + compression leggings<br />\n- cap +Fleece Neck gaiter, Fleece gloves<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基本上係感覺舒服既 再著多啲就會好唔方便 帽可以考慮換beanie個啲會再暖啲 <br />\nBackpack 就裝上面一部分gear 同三set內衣/襪打替換  <br />\n一條wool leggings 備用 一條普通長褲  &lt;--- 夜晚出去既話先會咁著<br />\n同埋一件普通tee for 室內 <br />\n基本上每日就係普住同一套衫<br />\n<br />\n淨低就裝<br />\n- 夠飽肚一日既乾糧 (protein bars / nuts) &lt;-- 呢個好重要，基本上就係我每日既午餐同埋徒步需要大量體力<br />\n- pasta (盡量自己煮唔食餐廳)<br />\n- 細水 (飲曬就再裝過)<br />\n- 頭燈 電筒 萬用刀 以備突發需要<br />\n- 我仲有帶電腦，書，同相機器材 (呢個因人而異 唔影相可以睡袋同營具 不過就小心啲 個邊有official camping area)<br />\n<br />\n以上加埋約18kg <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9338b7d4918d03dec16c7068605f792c220a53fd","tid":1185435,"uid":64547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8af2dcd242debd6f59fed6d8a16ef732bbdf8842","tid":1185435,"uid":6800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T14:41:38.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n二月去咗十日剩係南部+西島<br />\n真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想夏天再去環島<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T09:59:08.000Z","msg":"二月聽朋友講有段時間係極光大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無睇到 <br />\n夏天最想去 Landmannalaugar <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4038677ee4dfb0fc1880f6384d10df1e196dc7","tid":1185435,"uid":64547,"li