service 只係一種旅行方式  <br />\n好多時都係出於同情心同埋你情我願 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有同佢地講其實截唔到順風車/每當俾佢地pass過其實有啲尷尬<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">可能我毒撚心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(亞洲人同外國人思想分別)</span><br />\n佢地反而覺得呢樣野其實好平常 有幾架車仲要主動停低問我 &quot;do you need a ride?&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲車主仲同我講自己當初都係hitchhiker <br />\n佢地無care咁多咩道德咩義務個啲 好有遇見不平拔刀相助既感覺 不過呢啲只係肯接hitchhiker既人既諗法啦 同埋好睇本身住既地方文化係點<br />\n試過有次係hostel 相認返一個 pass 過我既美國人 佢同我講有猶豫過應唔應該停車好 但因為美國唔係一個 car stopping country 車陌生人係一件相當危險既事 (發生過好多robbery 同murder case) 所以之後都明白原來有部分唔停車既人其實係feel insecure"},{"pid":"3c9982f14613d64f946ee70bb7a3988b7296c4df","tid":1185435,"uid":6800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9338b7d4918d03dec16c7068605f792c220a53fd","tid":1185435,"uid":64547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8af2dcd242debd6f59fed6d8a16ef732bbdf8842","tid":1185435,"uid":6800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T14:41:38.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n二月去咗十日剩係南部+西島<br />\n真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想夏天再去環島<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T09:59:08.000Z","msg":"二月聽朋友講有段時間係極光大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無睇到 <br />\n夏天最想去 Landmannalaugar <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:20:45.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n住Hof個晚撞正KP5+無雲<br />\n食完飯行出去望上個天就已經見到整片白光周圍走<br />\n導遊話暫時係今年最強嘅極光<br />\n<br />\n雖然個晚大概-10度<br />\n但真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢一世都會記得個景象<br />\n<br />\n不過去blue ice cave撞正厚雪<br />\n入面睇唔係好藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/s